Description: Core configuration and branding for CTX OS.
 This package provides the foundational overlay for the CTX OS 
 environment. It includes system-wide performance tuning for 
 PostgreSQL, custom shell configurations, desktop environment 
 branding for XFCE and KDE, and developer templates.
